#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I set Firefox as my default browser?"
msgstr "Kako lahko Firefox nastavim kot privzeti brskalnik?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You want to click on a link in &kmail; and "
"have the link opened in <application>Firefox</application>. At the moment, "
"another browser is used. You want to change this."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> Želite klikniti na povezavo v &kmail;-u in "
"povezavo odpreti v <application>Firefox</application>. Trenutno se za to "
"uporablja drug brskalnik. To želite spremeniti."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> This change will affect all of &kde;, not "
"just &kmail;. Select <menuchoice> <guimenu>&systemsettings;</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Default Applications</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Web "
"Browser</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Mozilla Firefox</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> Ta sprememba bo vplivala na celoten &kde;, ne "
"le na &kmail;. Izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>&systemsettings;</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Privzete aplikacije</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Spletni "
"brskalnik</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Mozilla Firefox</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are an administrator and want to make this setting automatically for "
"your users, do this."
msgstr ""
"Če ste skrbnik in želite to nastavitev za svoje uporabnike nastaviti "
"samodejno, storite to."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Run <screen># qtpaths --paths ConfigLocation</screen> in a terminal. This "
"will display the path(s) leading to configuration files for KDE programs in "
"your system. Use the path starting in each user's Home directory, and locate "
"the file named <filename>kdeglobals</filename>, then add this line under "
"category <guilabel>[General]</guilabel>:"
msgstr ""
"V terminalu zaženite <screen># qtpaths --paths ConfigLocation</screen>. "
"Prikazane bodo poti do nastavitvenih datotek za programe KDE v vašem "
"sistemu. Uporabite pot, ki se začne v domačem imeniku vsakega uporabnika, in "
"poiščite datoteko z imenom <filename>kdeglobals</filename>, nato dodajte to "
"vrstico v kategorijo <guilabel>[General]</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: faq.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "BrowserApplication[$e]=firefox.desktop"
msgstr "BrowserApplication[$e]=firefox.desktop"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also try the script in <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:"
"myLanguage/Tutorials/Modify_KDE_Software_Defaults\">Tutorials/ "
"Modify_KDE_Software_Defaults</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Poskusite lahko tudi s skriptom na <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/"
"Special:myLanguage/Tutorials/Modify_KDE_Software_Defaults\">Tutorials/ "
"Modify_KDE_Software_Defaults</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The actual physical location of configuration variables is distribution "
"dependent. Do not be surprised if some of the instructions about modifying "
"configuration variables documented in the &kde; wiki will not work for you. "
"The public forum (online) for your distro is a good place to seek help."
msgstr ""
"Dejanska fizična lokacija konfiguracijskih spremenljivk je odvisna od "
"distribucije. Ne bodite presenečeni, če nekatera navodila za spreminjanje "
"konfiguracijskih spremenljivk, ki so dokumentirana v wikiju &kde;, ne bodo "
"delovala za vas. Javni forum (na spletu) za vašo distribucijo je dober kraj, "
"kjer lahko poiščete pomoč."

