#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I control my Roaming profile's connection?"
msgstr "Kako nadzorujem povezavo svojega profila gostovanja?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You set up a <emphasis>Roaming profile</"
"emphasis> so you can access your home server while you are on the road, but "
"it keeps trying to connect even when you are at home. Auto-connection is "
"disabled in the setup screens."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> Nastavili ste <emphasis>profil gostovanja</"
"emphasis>, da lahko do domačega strežnika dostopate, ko ste na poti, vendar "
"se poskuša povezati tudi, ko ste doma. Samodejna povezava je v nastavitvenih "
"zaslonih onemogočena."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure KMail</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Accounts</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Receiving (tab)</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>(select "
"the account to exclude)</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Retrieval Options</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, then uncheck <guilabel>Include in Manual Mail "
"Check</guilabel>. This will exclude that profile when you hit the download "
"icon, but the account will still be available from the drop-down list, "
"making it easy to retrieve your mail when away from home."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> Pojdite v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi KMail</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Računi</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Prejemanje (zavihek)</guimenuitem> "
"<guimenuitem>(izberite račun, ki ga želite izključiti)</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Možnosti pridobivanja</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, "
"nato odstranite kljukico <guilabel>Vključi v ročno preverjanje pošte</"
"guilabel>. Ko pritisnete ikono za prenos, bo ta profil izključen, vendar bo "
"račun še vedno na voljo na spustnem seznamu, kar vam bo olajšalo prevzemanje "
"pošte, ko boste odsotni od doma."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I store sent messages in a special folder?"
msgstr "Kako shranjujem poslana sporočila v posebni mapi?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You want to store the messages you have sent "
"in a special folder. Maybe you are using an &IMAP; server and wish to store "
"your sent mail on the server, not in a local folder."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> Sporočila, ki ste jih poslali, želite shraniti "
"v posebno mapo. Morda uporabljate strežnik &IMAP; in želite poslano pošto "
"shraniti v strežnik in ne v lokalno mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> In &kmail;, navigate to "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure KMail</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Identities</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>(Choose an "
"identity)</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Modify</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Advanced</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Sent-mail "
"folder</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and select the folder you want to use."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> V &kmail; pojdite na "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguracija KMail</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Identitete</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>(Izberite "
"identiteto)</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Spremeni</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Napredno</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Mapa poslanih "
"sporočil</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in izberite želeno mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can use the <guilabel>Sent-Mail Folder</guilabel> field "
"(accessible via the <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu in the composer window) to "
"override the default sent mail folder for a particular message."
msgstr ""
"Lahko pa uporabite tudi polje <guilabel>Mapa poslanih sporočil</guilabel> "
"(dostopno prek menija <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> v oknu skladatelja), da za "
"določeno sporočilo razveljavite privzeto mapo za poslano pošto."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I move trash email messages to a special folder?"
msgstr "Kako premaknem e-poštna sporočila v smeteh v posebno mapo?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You want to store trash in a special folder. "
"Maybe you are using an &IMAP; server and want trashed email messages to be "
"stored on the server, not locally."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> Smeti želite shraniti v posebno mapo. Morda "
"uporabljate strežnik &IMAP; in želite, da se zavržena e-poštna sporočila "
"shranijo v strežniku in ne lokalno."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> In the settings dialog select an &IMAP; "
"account on the <guilabel>Accounts</guilabel> page. Click on "
"<guibutton>Modify</guibutton> and change the trash folder location via the "
"<guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> V pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami izberite "
"račun &IMAP; na strani <guilabel>Računi</guilabel>. Kliknite "
"<guibutton>Spremeni</guibutton> in v zavihku <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel> "
"spremenite lokacijo mape za smeti."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I store encrypted messages in unencrypted form?"
msgstr "Kako lahko šifrirana sporočila shranim v nešifrirani obliki?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You exchange encrypted mail with a friend, but "
"would like to store your own copy unencrypted, once you have opened the "
"message."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> S prijateljem si izmenjujete šifrirano pošto, "
"vendar bi po odprtju sporočila radi shranili svojo lastno nešifrirano kopijo."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> To store emails that have been decrypted once "
"in unencrypted format thereafter, add this item to your <filename>kmail2rc</"
"filename> configuration file, in the [Reader] section:"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> Če želite elektronska sporočila, ki so bila "
"enkrat dešifrirana, nato shraniti v nešifrirani obliki, dodajte to postavko "
"v nastavitveno datoteko <filename>kmail2rc</filename> v razdelek [Reader]:"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>store-displayed-messages-unencrypted=true</userinput>."
msgstr "<userinput>store-displayed-messages-unencrypted=true</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I filter spam on an &IMAP; server?"
msgstr "Kako filtrirati neželeno pošto v strežniku &IMAP;?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You intend to read your mail from an &IMAP; "
"server, and wonder how filtering and spam handling will occur."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> Pošto nameravate brati iz strežnika &IMAP; in "
"se sprašujete, kako bo potekalo filtriranje in ravnanje z nezaželeno pošto."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> The machine that already has your mail can "
"become your &IMAP; server. You will have to configure a server application. "
"<application>Dovecot</application> is one such, and the guidance on the "
"project web pages make it relatively simple to set up. That still leaves you "
"with the problem of filtering, as it makes sense to do that on the server "
"(when you point &kmail; at the server you will see the folders that have "
"been created on that system). There are several options. One of the best "
"known is <application>Procmail</application>. Another one is "
"<application>Imapfilter</application>. There is plenty of information on the "
"internet about setting these up. Further discussion of these OSS packages is "
"beyond the scope of &kmail;'s documentation."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> Računalnik, ki že ima vašo pošto, lahko "
"postane vaš strežnik &IMAP;. Nastaviti boste morali strežniško aplikacijo. "
"<application>Dovecot</application> je ena takih aplikacij, ki jo je po "
"navodilih na spletnih straneh projekta razmeroma preprosto nastaviti. Še "
"vedno pa imate po tem težave s filtriranjem, ki ga je smiselno izvajati v "
"strežniku (ko usmerite &kmail; na strežnik, boste videli mape, ki so bile "
"ustvarjene v tem sistemu). Na voljo je več možnosti. Ena najbolj znanih je "
"<application>Procmail</application>. Druga aplikacija je "
"<application>Imapfilter</application>. Na spletu je na voljo veliko "
"informacij o njihovi vzpostavitvi. Nadaljnja razprava o teh paketih OSS "
"presega obseg dokumentacije &kmail;-a."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I get more screen space in &kmail;?"
msgstr "Kako lahko pridobim več prostora na zaslonu v storitvi &kmail;?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You are using &kmail; on a laptop or notebook, "
"and find that the new <emphasis>Aggregation</emphasis> display leaves you "
"too little screen space."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> Uporabljate &kmail; na prenosnem računalniku in "
"ugotavljate, da vam novi prikaz <emphasis>agregacije</emphasis> pušča "
"premalo prostora."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis>If you want to change the message list so each "
"message uses a single line instead of two lines, go to "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Message List</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Theme</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and change the theme to "
"<guilabel>Classic</guilabel>. If you want to disable grouping by date, "
"change the aggregation using <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Message List</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Aggregation</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> to <guilabel>Standard Mailing List</guilabel>. Now your &kmail; "
"will look exactly like it did in early versions of the program."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis>Če želite seznam sporočil spremeniti tako, da "
"bo vsako sporočilo uporabljalo eno vrstico namesto dveh, pojdite v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Seznam sporočil</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Tema</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in spremenite temo "
"v <guilabel>Klasična</guilabel>. Če želite onemogočiti združevanje po "
"datumu, spremenite združevanje z uporabo <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Seznam sporočil</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Združevanje</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> v <guilabel>Standarden dopisni seznam</guilabel>. "
"Zdaj bo vaš &kmail; videti tako, kot je bil videti v zgodnjih različicah "
"programa."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure &kmail;</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Appearance</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Fonts</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> you can select <guilabel>Use custom fonts</"
"guilabel> to change the setting for the message list. You can also set the "
"font size in the <guilabel>Use custom fonts</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"V <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavitve &kmail;-a</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Izgled</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Pisave</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> lahko izberete <guilabel>Uporabi pisave po meri</"
"guilabel> in spremenite nastavitev za seznam sporočil. Velikost pisave lahko "
"nastavite tudi v pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Uporabi pisave po meri</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I turn &kmail; folder tool tips off?"
msgstr "Kako lahko izklopim namige za mape orodja &kmail;?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You are using &kmail; on a laptop or notebook, "
"and find that the <emphasis>tooltips</emphasis> that pop up hide too many "
"folder names"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> Uporabljate &kmail; na prenosnem računalniku in "
"ugotavljate, da <emphasis>orodni namigi</emphasis>, ki se pojavljajo, "
"zakrivajo preveč imen map"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> Right-click on the \"Name\" header above the "
"<guilabel>Folder List</guilabel> and check <guilabel>Never</guilabel> under "
"<guilabel>Display Tooltips</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> Z desno tipko miške kliknite na glavo \"Ime\" "
"nad <guilabel>Seznamom map</guilabel> in v možnosti <guilabel>Prikaži orodne "
"namige</guilabel> označite <guilabel>Nikoli</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I hide the message list tool tips?"
msgstr "Kako lahko skrijem ordne namige na seznamu sporočil?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On &kmail;, <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure "
"KMail</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Appearance</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Message "
"List</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> tab, uncheck <menuchoice><guimenu>General</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Display tooltips for messages and group headers</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Na zavihku &kmail;, <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavitve KMaila</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Videz</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Saznam sporočil</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, "
"odstranite potrditev <menuchoice><guimenu>Splošno</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži orodne namige za sporočila in glave skupin</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, right-click one of the headers above the message list and "
"clear the check box labeled <guilabel>Display Tooltips</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost je, da z desno tipko miške kliknete eno od glav nad seznamom "
"sporočil in počistite potrditveno polje z oznako <guilabel>Prikaži orodne "
"namige</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The headers above the message list do not appear if you have chosen the "
"\"Smart\" theme."
msgstr ""
"Če ste izbrali temo \"Pametno\", se glave nad seznamom sporočil ne prikažejo."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How do I transfer my mail and settings to another computer (or to another "
"user account on the same machine)?"
msgstr ""
"Kako prenesem svojo pošto in nastavitve na drug računalnik (ali na drug "
"uporabniški račun na istem računalniku)?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Import/Export &kmail; "
"Data...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to import and export settings and data. "
"Please see <ulink url=\"help:/pimsettingexporter\">PIM Setting Exporter</"
"ulink> for details."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi/izvozi "
"podatke &kmail;-a</guimenuitem></menuchoice> za uvoz in izvoz nastavitev in "
"podatkov. Za podrobnosti glejte <ulink url=\"help:/pimsettingexporter\"> "
"Izvoznik nastavitev PIM</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why can't I copy my email folders to a USB stick?"
msgstr "Zakaj svojih e-poštnih map ne morem kopirati na ključek USB?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You are setting up a new computer and want to "
"transfer all your mail. You decide to copy everything to a USB stick. The "
"job starts, then you get a failure message:"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Težava:</emphasis> Nastavljate nov računalnik in želite prenesti "
"vso svojo pošto. Odločite se, da boste vse kopirali na USB ključek. Naloga "
"se začne izvajati, nato pa se prikaže sporočilo o napaki:"

#. Tag: screen
#: faq.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unable to copy ............ Invalid argument"
msgstr "Ni mogoče kopirati ............ Nepravilen argument"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> Your usb stick is <ulink url=\"http://wiki."
"linuxquestions.org/wiki/VFAT\">VFAT</ulink> formatted, and therefore it "
"can't handle <emphasis>maildir</emphasis> folder names (nor can it handle "
"<emphasis>permissions</emphasis>, which can cause many other problems). You "
"have two choices. Either format your <acronym>USB</acronym> stick as ext2 "
"(or ext3 / 4 -- in which case you should be aware it can't be read by "
"&Windows; without installing additional software) or create a .tar or .zip "
"file of your mail, then copy that to the stick and extract the archive on "
"the new host."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> Vaš USB ključ je <ulink url=\"http://wiki."
"linuxquestions.org/wiki/VFAT\">VFAT</ulink> formatiran, zato ne more "
"obdelati <emphasis>maildir</emphasis> imen map (prav tako ne more obdelati "
"<emphasis>dovoljenj</emphasis>, kar lahko povzroči številne druge težave). "
"Imate dve možnosti. Svoj <acronym>USB</acronym> ključek lahko formatirate "
"kot ext2 (ali ext3 / 4 - v tem primeru se morate zavedati, da ga &Windows; "
"ne more prebrati brez namestitve dodatne programske opreme) ali pa "
"ustvarite .tar ali .zip datoteko svoje pošte, ki jo nato kopirajte na "
"ključek in arhiv razširite na novem gostitelju."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Why are my filters not applied to incoming messages from &IMAP; accounts?"
msgstr ""
"Zakaj se moji filtri ne uporabljajo za dohodna sporočila iz računov &IMAP;?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Normal &IMAP; mode does not support filtering, but the new disconnected "
"&IMAP; account type does. You could try to use server-side filtering (ask "
"your admin how to install filters on the server, and in which format), since "
"&IMAP; is all about managing your email <emphasis>on the server</emphasis>. "
"See <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure &kmail;...</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Receiving</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>(some &IMAP; "
"account)</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, then click <guilabel>Modify...</"
"guilabel> and the <guilabel>Filtering</guilabel> tab to configure server "
"side filtering using the <ulink url=\"http://sieve.info/\">Sieve</ulink> "
"programming language (if your &IMAP; server supports it)."
msgstr ""
"Običajni način &IMAP; ne podpira filtriranja, nova nepovezana vrsta računa "
"&IMAP; pa ga podpira. Lahko poskusite uporabiti filtriranje na strani "
"strežnika (vprašajte skrbnika, kako namestiti filtre v strežnik in v kakšni "
"obliki), saj je &IMAP; namenjen upravljanju e-pošte <emphasis>na strežniku</"
"emphasis>. Oglejte si <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavitve &kmail;...</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Prejemanje</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>(nek &IMAP; "
"račun)</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, nato kliknite <guilabel>Spremeni...</"
"guilabel> in zavihek <guilabel>Filtiranje</guilabel>, da konfigurirate "
"filtriranje na strežniku z uporabo <ulink url=\"http://sieve.info/\">Sieve</"
"ulink> programskega jezika (če ga vaš &IMAP; strežnik podpira)."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"What should I know if I want to use <application>PGP</application>/"
"<application>GnuPG</application> with &kmail;?"
msgstr ""
"Kaj moram vedeti, če želim uporabljati <application>PGP</application>/"
"<application>GnuPG</application> s &kmail;?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; provides a simple and easy-to-use interface for the basic functions "
"of these programs; still, you should understand how these programs work, and "
"what might make their use insecure. Some important issues:"
msgstr ""
"&kmail; zagotavlja preprost in za uporabo enostaven vmesnik za osnovne "
"funkcije teh programov; kljub temu morate razumeti, kako ti programi "
"delujejo in kaj lahko povzroči, da njihova uporaba ni varna. Nekaj pomembnih "
"težav:"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You <emphasis>really</emphasis> should test if encryption works before you "
"use it. &kmail; partly relies on <application>PGP</application>/"
"<application>GnuPG</application>'s error strings, which often change between "
"different versions."
msgstr ""
"Preden začnete uporabljati šifriranje, morate <emphasis>resnično</emphasis> "
"preveriti, ali deluje. &kmail; delno se zanaša na nize napak "
"<application>PGP</application>/<application>GnuPG</application>, ki se med "
"različnimi različicami pogosto spreminjajo."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; will not encrypt messages with an untrusted (unsigned) public key. "
"If you want to encrypt to such a key you should check the identity of the "
"key owner and only then sign the key with your secret key. If you do not "
"want to or cannot check the identity of the key owner, but nevertheless want "
"to encrypt the message, then please sign the key locally with "
"<userinput><command>gpg</command> <option>--lsign</option> "
"<replaceable>keyID</replaceable></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; ne bo šifriral sporočil z nezaupljivim (nepodpisanim) javnim "
"ključem. Če želite šifrirati s takim ključem, morate preveriti identiteto "
"lastnika ključa in šele nato ključ podpisati s svojim skrivnim ključem. Če "
"ne želite ali ne morete preveriti identitete lastnika ključa, vendar kljub "
"temu želite šifrirati sporočilo, ključ podpišite lokalno z "
"<userinput><command>gpg</command> <option>--lsign</option> "
"<replaceable>keyID</replaceable></userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Trusting a foreign public key without checking it is not a good idea."
msgstr ""
"Zaupanje tujemu javnemu ključu, ne da bi ga preverili, ni dobra zamisel."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starting with GnuPG 1.0.7 you have to set your own key to ultimate owner "
"trust: it is no longer implicitly done for you."
msgstr ""
"Od različice GnuPG 1.0.7 naprej morate sami nastaviti ključ za končno "
"zaupanje lastniku: to ni več implicitno storjeno namesto vas."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "Where does &kmail; save my settings and my mail?"
msgstr "Kje &kmail; shrani moje nastavitve in pošto?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most &kmail; settings are stored in <filename>~/.config/kmail2rc</"
"filename>&nbsp;."
msgstr ""
"Večina nastavitev &kmail;-a je shranjena v <filename>~/.config/kmail2rc</"
"filename>&nbsp;."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Akonadi</emphasis>-controlled entries are stored in these "
"folders:"
msgstr ""
"V teh mapah so shranjeni vnosi, ki jih nadzoruje <emphasis>Akonadi</"
"emphasis>:"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "<filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share/</filename>."
msgstr "<filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "<filename class=\"directory\">~/.config/akonadi/</filename>."
msgstr "<filename class=\"directory\">~/.config/akonadi/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that some of the files are hidden: remember to also copy those if you "
"want to backup or archive your mails. To be safe, use <ulink url=\"help:/"
"pimdataexporter\">PIM Data Exporter</ulink> to back up your mail and your "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da so nekatere datoteke skrite: če želite varnostno kopirati "
"ali arhivirati pošto, ne pozabite kopirati tudi teh datotek. Za varnost "
"uporabite <ulink url=\"help:/pimdataexporter\">Izvažanje nastavitev PIM</"
"ulink> za varnostno kopiranje pošte in nastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why did &kmail; regenerate the index of a folder?"
msgstr "Zakaj je &kmail; obnovil kazalo mape?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; regenerates the index of a folder whenever the index appears to be "
"out of date, &ie; whenever the contents of a folder are newer than the "
"index. &kmail; regenerates the index in this case in order to prevent the "
"loss or corruption of messages."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; obnovi indeks mape, kadar koli se zdi, da je kazalo zastarelo, &ie; "
"kadar koli je vsebina mape novejša od kazala. &kmail; v tem primeru obnovi "
"kazalo, da bi preprečil izgubo ali poškodbo sporočil."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "An outdated index can have several causes; these are the most common."
msgstr "Zastarelo kazalo ima lahko več vzrokov, ti so najpogostejši."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some other program modified the contents of the folder. If you want to use "
"&kmail; together with procmail then please read <link linkend=\"faq-procmail"
"\">this &FAQ;</link>. If you want to use &kmail; together with another email "
"client then please read <link linkend=\"faq-other-muas\">this &FAQ;</link>."
msgstr ""
"Nek drug program je spremenil vsebino mape. Če želite uporabljati &kmail; "
"skupaj s procmailom, preberite <link linkend=\"faq-procmail\">ta &FAQ; "
"(pogosta vprašanja)</link>. Če želite &kmail; uporabljati skupaj z drugim "
"odjemalcem e-pošte, preberite <link linkend=\"faq-other-muas\">ta &FAQ; "
"(pogosta vprašanja)</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your mail folder is on a volume which is mounted via NFS, and if the "
"clock in the NFS server is behind the clock in your computer, then the NFS "
"server sometimes reports the wrong file date for the index file. In this "
"case &kmail; concludes that the index is outdated, although in reality it is "
"not. To fix this problem you (or your system administrator) have to make "
"sure that the clock in the NFS server and the clock in your computer are "
"always in sync. One way to achieve this is to use the ntp daemon."
msgstr ""
"Če je poštna mapa na nosilcu, ki je nameščen prek sistema NFS, in če ura v "
"strežniku NFS zaostaja za uro v računalniku, strežnik NFS včasih sporoči "
"napačen datum datoteke za datoteko kazala. V tem primeru &kmail; ugotovi, da "
"je kazalo zastarelo, čeprav v resnici ni. Če želite odpraviti to težavo, "
"morate vi (ali skrbnik sistema) poskrbeti, da sta ura v strežniku NFS in ura "
"v vašem računalniku vedno sinhronizirani. Eden od načinov za to je uporaba "
"ozadnjega programa ntp."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why doesn't &kmail; start up?"
msgstr "Zakaj se &kmail; ne zažene?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You want to start &kmail; from a minimal "
"desktop environment like <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Fvwm2\">fvwm2</ulink>. It does not start."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>težava:</emphasis> Želite zagnati &kmail; iz strnjenega namiznega "
"okolja, kot je <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fvwm2\">fvwm2</"
"ulink>. Ne zažene se."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> This happens because you are missing "
"<emphasis>dbus</emphasis> functionality. Start &kmail; from a terminal "
"window using dbus-launch, like this:"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Rešitev:</emphasis> To se zgodi, ker vam manjka funkcionalnost "
"<emphasis>dbus</emphasis>. V terminalskem oknu zaženite &kmail; s programom "
"dbus-launch, kot sledi:"

#. Tag: screen
#: faq.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "# dbus-launch kmail"
msgstr "# dbus-launch kmail"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Can I use &kmail; together with a different email client, &eg;, "
"<application>mutt</application>?"
msgstr ""
"Ali lahko &kmail; uporabljam skupaj z drugim odjemalcem e-pošte, &eg;, "
"<application>mutt</application>?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you're using the mbox format for your folders it is not possible to use a "
"different email client while &kmail; is running. With <application>mutt</"
"application>, there may also be problems even if both programs are not "
"running at the same time. We recommend you use the maildir format if you "
"want to use mutt with &kmail;."
msgstr ""
"Če za svoje mape uporabljate format mbox, med delovanjem programa &kmail; ni "
"mogoče uporabljati drugega odjemalca e-pošte. Pri programu "
"<application>mutt</application> lahko pride do težav, tudi če oba programa "
"nista zagnana hkrati. Če želite uporabljati mutt s &kmail;-om, vam "
"priporočamo uporabo formata maildir."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I convert my mailboxes from mbox to maildir?"
msgstr "Kako lahko pretvorim svoje poštne predale iz mboxa v maildir?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is no automated way to do that. You must create a new folder in "
"maildir format, then copy the messages from the mbox folder into this new "
"folder. Remember to adapt any filter rules connected with the old folder "
"before you delete it."
msgstr ""
"Za to ni samodejnega načina. Ustvariti morate novo mapo v obliki maildir, "
"nato pa sporočila iz mape mbox kopirati v to novo mapo. Preden izbrišete "
"staro mapo, ne pozabite prilagoditi vseh pravil filtriranja, povezanih z njo."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How can I remove attachments from a message without removing the message "
"itself?"
msgstr ""
"Kako lahko odstranim priponke iz sporočila, ne da bi odstranil sporočilo "
"samo?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the context menu with a &RMB; click on an attachment and select "
"<guimenuitem>Delete Attachment</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Odprite kontekstni meni z &RMB; kliknite priponko in izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Izbriši priponko</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I make &kmail; check for new messages at startup?"
msgstr ""
"Kako lahko nastavim, da &kmail; ob zagonu preverja obstoj novih sporočil?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &kmail; should always check for new messages at startup then enable "
"<guilabel>Check mail on startup</guilabel> on the <link linkend=\"configure-"
"accounts-receiving\">Accounts configuration page</link>. Alternatively, "
"start &kmail; with <command>kmail <option>--check</option></command>."
msgstr ""
"Če želit, da &kmail; ob zagonu vedno preveri za nova sporočila, potem "
"omogočite <guilabel>Preveri pošto ob zagonu</guilabel> na <link linkend="
"\"configure-accounts-receiving\">Strani za nastavitve računov</link>. Druga "
"možnost je, da zaženete &kmail; z ukazom <command>kmail <option>--check</"
"option></command>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Where can I find a list of changes between one version of &kmail; and the "
"next one?"
msgstr ""
"Kje lahko najdem seznam sprememb med eno različico programa &kmail; in "
"naslednjo različico?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The welcome screen lists all important changes for your version. It is "
"displayed when you select <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>&kmail; Introduction</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Na pozdravnem zaslonu so navedene vse pomembne spremembe za vašo različico. "
"Prikaže se, ko izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>&kmail; Uvod</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I'm one of those people whose messages consist of 100 quoted lines and one "
"line written by myself. For some odd reason, this annoys other people. Can "
"&kmail; help me and make everyone's life better?"
msgstr ""
"Sem eden onih, ki poleg stotih citiranih vrstic doda še eno ali dve svoji. "
"Zaradi nekega čudnega razloga (pojma nimam, katerega) nekatere ljudi to hudo "
"moti. Mi &kmail; zmore pomagati ter vsem polepšati življenje?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sure. Just select a short, relevant piece of the original message with the "
"mouse before you click \"reply\". Only this part of the original message "
"will be quoted by the composer."
msgstr ""
"Jasno. Pred odgovarjanjem z miško preprosto označite del prvotnega besedila. "
"V odgovoru bo citiran zgolj označeni odlomek."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Why do some messages exhibit a value of \"unknown\" in the <guilabel>Date</"
"guilabel> field? Why is the date sometimes incorrect?"
msgstr ""
"Zakaj imajo nekatera sporočila v polju <guilabel>Datum</guilabel> vrednost "
"\"neznano\"? Zakaj je datum včasih napačen?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most likely, the \"Date:\" header of these messages is broken and &kmail; "
"cannot interpret it. That is not a bug in &kmail;, but in the software that "
"sent the mail."
msgstr ""
"Najverjetneje je naslov \"Datum:\" teh sporočil pokvarjen in si ga &kmail; "
"ne more razlagati. To ni napaka v &kmail;-u, temveč v programski opremi, ki "
"je poslala pošto."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid "My signature has two dashes above it. What's up?"
msgstr "Moj podpis ima nad seboj dva pomišljaja. Kaj se dogaja?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Separating the signature from the message body with two dashes and a space "
"on a single line is common usage. These symbols permit mail clients that "
"recognize them to trim the signature from a reply. If your signature does "
"not include this separator, &kmail; will automatically add it."
msgstr ""
"Ločevanje podpisa od jedra sporočila z dvema pomišljajema je splošen in "
"uporaben standard. Ta simbola omogočata poštnim odjemalcem, ki ju "
"prepoznajo, da iz odgovora izrežejo podpis. Če podpis ne vsebuje teh ločil, "
"ga ju &kmail; samodejno dodal."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid "Are there any known bugs in &kmail;?"
msgstr "Obstajajo kakšni znani hrošči v &kmail;?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are quite a few, as you can see by querying the &kmail; <ulink url="
"\"https://bugs.kde.org/buglist.cgi?quicksearch=kmail2\">Bugzilla page</"
"ulink>. As of this writing (April, 2021) roughly 70% of the reported bugs "
"are unconfirmed, or irreproducible. All in all we think &kmail; is a robust "
"piece of software."
msgstr ""
"Teh je kar nekaj, kot lahko vidite s poizvedbo po &kmail; <ulink url="
"\"https://bugs.kde.org/buglist.cgi?quicksearch=kmail2\">Strani Bugzilla</"
"ulink>. Do trenutka pisanja tega članka (april 2021) je približno 70 % "
"prijavljenih napak nepotrjenih ali neponovljivih. Na splošno menimo, da je "
"&kmail; robustna programska oprema."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should not run &kmail; while another email client is already accessing "
"the files in the mail directory; if you do, you may lose messages. Note that "
"you should make backups of your messages -- and all your important data -- "
"regularly. That's just good digital hygiene."
msgstr ""
"Ne smete zagnati programa &kmail;, medtem ko drug odjemalec e-pošte že "
"dostopa do datotek v poštnem imeniku; če to storite, lahko izgubite "
"sporočila. Upoštevajte, da morate redno izdelovati varnostne kopije sporočil "
"in vseh pomembnih podatkov. To je dobra digitalna higiena."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why doesn't &kmail; display &HTML; mail properly?"
msgstr "Zakaj &kmail; ne prikaže &HTML; pošte pravilno?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"References to external content, like images, are disabled by default, as "
"spammers can use them to track whether and when you read a message. Loading "
"external references can be activated in the <guilabel>Security</guilabel> "
"tab in &kmail;'s configuration dialog. Plugins (like <trademark class="
"\"registered\">Adobe</trademark> <application>Flash</application>), &Java; "
"and JavaScript will not be displayed in &kmail; for security reasons, and "
"there is no way to activate them."
msgstr ""
"Sklicevanja na zunanjo vsebino, kot so slike, so privzeto onemogočena, saj "
"lahko pošiljatelji neželene pošte z njimi spremljajo, ali in kdaj ste "
"prebrali sporočilo. Nalaganje zunanjih povezavS lahko aktivirate v zavihku "
"<guilabel>Varnost</guilabel> v pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo storitve "
"&kmail;. Vtičniki (kot so <trademark class=\"registered\">Adobe</trademark> "
"<application>Flash</application>), &Java; in JavaScript iz varnostnih "
"razlogov ne bodo prikazani v &kmail;-u in jih ni mogoče aktivirati."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Can I use two different versions of &kmail; at the same time? Can I go back "
"from a current version of &kmail; to an older one?"
msgstr ""
"Lahko naenkrat uporabljam dve različni verziji &kmail;-a? Ali lahko trenutno "
"različico &kmail;-a zamenjam s starejšo?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should only run one instance of &kmail; at a time. We also recommend "
"that you stick to a certain version and not switch back and forth between "
"different versions. Downgrading to an older version may work, but will "
"probably cause problems because, for instance, the index file formats have "
"been changed. Upgrading should never be a problem."
msgstr ""
"Naenkrat lahko poganjaš le eno verzijo &kmail;. Priporočamo tudi, da se "
"držite določene različice in ne preklapljate med različnimi različicami. "
"Prenova na starejšo različico lahko deluje, vendar bo verjetno povzročila "
"težave, ker so se na primer spremenile oblike indeksnih datotek. Nadgradnja "
"nikoli ne bi smela biti težava."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "Does &kmail; support uuencoded files?"
msgstr "Ali &kmail; podpira datoteke uuencoded?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Uuencoded attachments are not supported. Save mail with uuencoded "
"attachments, then use <command>uudecode</command> to decode the attachments."
msgstr ""
"Nepodprte so priponke z oznako uuencoded. Shranite pošto z uuenkodiranimi "
"priponkami, nato pa uporabite ukaz <command>uudecode</command> za "
"dekodiranje priponk."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; crashed while I was composing a message. Is that message lost now?"
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija &kmail; se je sesula med pisanjem sporočila. Je sporočilo sedaj "
"izgubljeno?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; tries to save your mail to <filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/"
"share/kmail2/autosave/</filename> in case of a crash. The next time you "
"start &kmail; the mail composer should appear with your message again; If it "
"does not, try to open the files in <filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/"
"share/kmail2/autosave/</filename> with an editor. If there are no files in "
"that folder then the crash was so bad that &kmail; could not save your "
"message."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; poskuša vašo pošto v primeru okvare shraniti v <filename class="
"\"directory\">~/.local/share/kmail2/autosave/</filename>. Ko naslednjič "
"zaženete &kmail;, bi se moral skladatelj pošte spet prikazati z vašim "
"sporočilom; če se to ne zgodi, poskusite odpreti datoteke v <filename class="
"\"directory\">~/.local/share/kmail2/autosave/</filename> z nekim "
"urejevalnikom. Če v tej mapi ni nobenih datotek, je bila nesreča tako huda, "
"da &kmail; ni mogel shraniti vašega sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I set up a folder to be mailing list aware, but messages from the list "
"aren't being saved in that folder. What's wrong?"
msgstr ""
"Nastavil sem mapo, ki se zaveda poštnega seznama, vendar se sporočila s "
"seznama ne shranjujejo v to mapo. Kaj je narobe?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Associating a folder with a mailing list has nothing to do with filtering "
"the mailing list messages &mdash; you have to add a new filter rule "
"manually. However, once you have associated a folder with a mailing list you "
"can use <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reply to Mailing-"
"List...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>New Message to Mailing-List...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> and the mailing list address will be set in the <guilabel>To:</"
"guilabel> field."
msgstr ""
"Povezovanje mape s poštnim seznamom nima nič skupnega s filtriranjem "
"sporočil poštnega seznama &mdash; ročno morate dodati novo pravilo za "
"filtriranje. Ko pa ste mapo enkrat povezali s poštnim seznamom, lahko "
"uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odgovori "
"poštnemu seznamu...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo sporočilo poštnemu "
"seznamu...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in v polju <guilabel>Za:</guilabel> se "
"bo nastavil naslov poštnega seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "My SMTP server requires authentication. Does &kmail; support this?"
msgstr ""
"Moj SMTP strežnik zahteva preverjanje pristnosti. Ali &kmail; to podpira?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Authentication</guilabel> can be set in the <guilabel>Advanced</"
"guilabel> tab of the <link linkend=\"configure-accounts-sending\">SMTP "
"configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Overitev</guilabel> lahko nastavite v zavihku <guilabel>napredno</"
"guilabel> v <link linkend=\"configure-accounts-sending\">Pogovornem oknu "
"konfiguracije SMTP</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use &kmail; and <application>procmail</application>?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam &kmail; in <application>procmail</application>?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, but it is important to do it the right way or you might lose mail. To "
"use <application>procmail</application> and &kmail; you must set up &kmail; "
"to fetch new mail from the spoolfiles in which <application>procmail</"
"application> drops your mail. Do <emphasis>not</emphasis> set up procmail to "
"deliver mail to a &kmail; folder. This cannot work."
msgstr ""
"Seveda! Vendar bodi pazljiv pri nastavljanju, sicer lahko izgubiš vso pošto. "
"Da bi spravil &kmail; in <application>procmail</application> k sodelovanju, "
"moraš nastaviti &kmail; tako, da sporočila jemlje iz datotek, kamor jih "
"<application>procmail</application> odlaga. <emphasis>Nikakor</emphasis> ne "
"poskušaj nastaviti procmaila, da bi sporočila dostavljal v mapo &kmail;-a - "
"to preprosto ne more delovati."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each procmail spoolfile you must then create an account from which "
"&kmail; will fetch new mail. You also need to specify the right lockfile "
"name for this account. When setting up an account, &kmail; will do some "
"minimal parsing on your <filename>.procmail</filename> file, and will try to "
"list every spoolfile it has found, and also the lockfiles next to the "
"<guilabel>procmail lockfile</guilabel> item. Procmail lets the user specify "
"lockfiles in three different ways, so there is no way to establish a "
"correspondence between the spoolfiles and lockfiles; it's really up to you "
"to make sure the right lockfile for each spoolfile has been specified."
msgstr ""
"Za vsako datoteko procmail vmesne shrambe morate nato ustvariti račun, iz "
"katerega bo &kmail; pobiral novo pošto. Za ta račun morate določiti tudi "
"pravo ime zaklepne datoteke. Pri vzpostavljanju računa bo &kmail; opravil "
"nekaj minimalnih pregledov datoteke <filename>.procmail</filename> in "
"poskusil našteti vse najdene datoteke vmesne shrambe ter tudi zaklepne "
"datoteke ob elementu <guilabel>zklepne datoteke procmail</guilabel>. "
"Procmail uporabniku omogoča, da določi zaklepne datoteke na tri različne "
"načine, zato ni mogoče določiti povezave med datotekami vmesne shrambe in "
"zaklepnimi datotekami, in zato morate sami poskrbeti, da je za vsako "
"datoteko vmesne shrambe določena prava zaklepna datoteka."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spellchecking does not recognize non-English characters. Why?"
msgstr "Preverjanje pravopisa ne prepozna neangleških znakov. Zakaj?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before you can use spellchecking, you must configure it. You can do so in "
"the composer window, under <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Spellchecker...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. You can "
"choose a dictionary there."
msgstr ""
"Preden lahko uporabite preverjanje pravopisa, ga morate nastaviti. To lahko "
"storite v oknu skladatelja pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Preveri črkovanje...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Tam "
"lahko izberete slovar."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How do I use my <application>Eudora</application>/&Netscape;/"
"<application>Outlook</application>/... mail folders in &kmail;?"
msgstr ""
"Kako lahko uporabljam svoje <application>Eudora</application>/&Netscape;/"
"<application>Outlook</application>/... poštne mape v &kmail;-u?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See the section <link linkend=\"importing-options\">Restore and Import in "
"&kmail;</link>."
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si razdelek <link linkend=\"importing-options\">Obnovitev in uvoz v "
"&kmail;</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Can I use encryption with my normal (non-<acronym>SSL</acronym>) POP3 "
"account?"
msgstr ""
"Lahko uporabljam kodiranje z normalnim (ne-<acronym>SSL</acronym>) POP3 "
"računom?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your POP3 server runs an <application>ssh</application> daemon, you can "
"use ssh to tunnel your POP3 connection using the following command:"
msgstr ""
"Če vaš POP3 strežnik poganja ozadnji program<application>ssh</application>, "
"ga lahko uporabite za prenos POP3 povezave z naslednjimi ukazi:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: faq.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>ssh</command> <option>-L 11000:127.0.0.1:110 user@host</option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>ssh</command> <option>-L 11000:127.0.0.1:110 user@host</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Modify your &kmail; configuration to fetch the mail via POP3 from "
"<userinput>localhost</userinput> and ssh will tunnel the connection for you."
msgstr ""
"Spremenite konfiguracijo &kmail;-a za prevzem pošte prek POP3 iz "
"<userinput>localhost</userinput> in ssh bo za vas tuneliral povezavo."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If non-encrypted messages have already been sent via the Internet, the only "
"advantage of using <application>ssh</application> is that your "
"<emphasis>password</emphasis> will be sent encrypted to the POP3 server."
msgstr ""
"Če so bila nešifrirana sporočila že poslana prek interneta, je edina "
"prednost uporabe <application>ssh</application> ta, da bo vaše "
"<emphasis>geslo</emphasis> v strežnik POP3 poslano šifrirano."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more details on setting up ssh, see <ulink url=\"http://www.faqs.org/"
"docs/Linux-mini/Secure-POP+SSH.html\">this web page</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več podrobnosti o nastavitvi ssh glejte <ulink url=\"http://www.faqs.org/"
"docs/Linux-mini/Secure-POP+SSH.html\">to spletno stran</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid "Does &kmail; lock the folders it uses?"
msgstr "Ali &kmail; uporabljane mape zaklepa?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; does not lock the files in <filename class=\"directory\">~.local/"
"share</filename>."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; ne zaklepa datotek v <filename class=\"directory\">~.local/share</"
"filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To avoid the risk of losing mail <emphasis>when using a local account,</"
"emphasis> it is necessary to ensure that &kmail; uses the same locking "
"mechanism as your mail delivery agent."
msgstr ""
"Da bi se izognili nevarnosti izgube pošte <emphasis>pri uporabi lokalnega "
"računa,</emphasis> je treba zagotoviti, da &kmail; uporablja enak mehanizem "
"zaklepanja kot vaš agent za dostavo pošte."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are five different locking options you can use:"
msgstr "Uporabite lahko pet različnih možnosti zaklepanja:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: faq.docbook:567
#, no-c-format
msgid "Procmail lockfile"
msgstr "Zaklepna datoteka Procmail"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: faq.docbook:568
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mutt dotlock"
msgstr "Zaklepna datoteka Mutt"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: faq.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mutt dotlock privileged"
msgstr "Privilegirana zaklepna datoteka Mutt"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>FCNTL</guilabel> (default)"
msgstr "<guilabel>FCNTL</guilabel> (privzeto)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: faq.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "none (use with care)"
msgstr "noben (uporabljajte previdno)"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Procmail lockfile</guilabel> uses a small utility that comes with "
"<application>procmail</application> called <command>lockfile</command>. You "
"can use this if your mail folder is in a folder where you have write "
"permission. This will not work on your <filename class=\"directory\">/var/"
"spool/mail/user</filename> file in most cases. It will create <filename>."
"lock</filename> files on your account when &kmail; is checking for new mail. "
"Please note that this will only work if <application>procmail</application> "
"is installed on your system."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Procmail zaklepna datoteka</guilabel> uporablja majhen pripomoček, "
"ki je priložen <application>procmail</application>, imenovan "
"<command>zaklepna datoteka</command>. To lahko uporabite, če je poštna mapa "
"v mapi, v kateri imate dovoljenje za pisanje. To v večini primerov ne bo "
"delovalo v datoteki <filename class=\"directory\">/var/spool/mail/user</"
"filename>. Ko bo &kmail; preverjal novo pošto, bo v vašem računu ustvaril "
"datoteke <filename>.lock</filename>. Upoštevajte, da bo to delovalo le, če "
"je v vašem sistemu nameščena <application>procmail</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Mutt dotlock</guilabel> and <guilabel>Mutt dotlock privileged</"
"guilabel> both use a small utility that comes with <application>mutt</"
"application> called <command>mutt_dotlock</command>. <guilabel>Mutt dotlock</"
"guilabel> can be used in the same way as the <guilabel>Procmail lockfile</"
"guilabel> option, with the same limitation with respect to the <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/var/spool/mail/</filename> folders. The <guilabel>Mutt "
"dotlock privileged</guilabel> option can create lock files in the <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/var/spool/mail</filename> folder. "
"<command>mutt_dotlock</command> is a setgid program and this option will run "
"it in setgid mode. Please note that these options will only work if "
"<application>mutt</application> is installed on your system."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zaklepna datoteka Mutt</guilabel> in <guilabel>Privilegirano "
"zaklepanje z zaklepno datoteko Mutt</guilabel> uporabljata majhen "
"pripomoček, ki je priložen <application>mutt</application>, imenovan "
"<command>mutt_dotlock</command>. <guilabel>Zaklepno datoteko Mutt</guilabel> "
"lahko uporabite enako kot možnost <guilabel>zaklepno datoteko Procmail</"
"guilabel>, z enako omejitvijo glede map <filename class=\"directory\">/var/"
"spool/mail/</filename>. Možnost <guilabel>Privilegirano zaklepanje z "
"zaklepno datoteko Mutt</guilabel> lahko ustvari datoteke s ključavnicami v "
"mapi <filename class=\"directory\">/var/spool/mail</filename>. "
"<command>mutt_dotlock</command> je program setgid in ta možnost ga zažene v "
"načinu setgid. Upoštevajte, da te možnosti delujejo le, če je v vašem "
"sistemu nameščena <application>mutt</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>FCNTL</guilabel> uses the <function>fcntl()</function> system call."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>FCNTL</guilabel> uporablja sistemski klic <function>fcntl()</"
"function>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using FCNTL locking might cause system lockups when the mail spool file is "
"on an NFS mounted device."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba zaklepanja FCNTL lahko povzroči blokado sistema, če je poštna "
"datoteka vmesne shrambe na napravi, nameščeni na NFS."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not want to use any locking, the <guilabel>none</guilabel> option "
"is available. However, there are risks of losing mail when no locking is "
"used."
msgstr ""
"Če ne želite uporabljati zaklepanja, je na voljo možnost <guilabel>none</"
"guilabel>. Vendar, če se ne uporablja zaklepanje, obstaja tveganje izgube "
"pošte."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I leave messages on the POP3 server?"
msgstr "Kako pustim sporočila v strežniku POP3?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to leave all messages on the server, open the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kmail;...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> window. Click on the <guilabel>Accounts</"
"guilabel> page. Select your account from the account list and click the "
"<guibutton>Modify...</guibutton> button. This dialog contains the "
"<guilabel>Leave fetched messages on the server</guilabel> setting (Advanced "
"tab) which you can enable."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vsa sporočila pustiti v strežniku, odprite okno "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavitve &kmail;...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Kliknite na stran <guilabel>Računi</guilabel>. S "
"seznama računov izberite svoj račun in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Spremeni...</"
"guibutton>. To pogovorno okno vsebuje nastavitev <guilabel>Pustiti prejeta "
"sporočila v strežniku</guilabel> (zavihek Napredno), ki jo lahko omogočite."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:620
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I automatically insert a text footer within my messages?"
msgstr "Kako lahko samodejno vstavim nogo besedila v sporočila?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The text footer is also called a signature (not to be confused with a "
"cryptographic signature). Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &kmail;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Look in the "
"<guilabel>Identity</guilabel> page for the <guilabel>Signature</guilabel> "
"tab and add your signature there. Then go to the <guilabel>General</"
"guilabel> tab on the <guilabel>Composer</guilabel> page and enable <xref "
"linkend=\"configure-composer-general-append-signature\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Besedilo v nogi se imenuje tudi podpis (ne smemo ga zamenjati s "
"kriptografskim podpisom). Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Nastavi &kmail;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Na strani "
"<guilabel>Identiteta</guilabel> poiščite zavihek <guilabel>Podpis</guilabel> "
"in tam dodajte svoj podpis. Nato pojdite na zavihek <guilabel>Splošno</"
"guilabel> na strani <guilabel>Skladatelj</guilabel> in omogočite <xref "
"linkend=\"configure-composer-general-append-signature\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How do I set up &Sendmail; to work with &kmail; if I have a dial-up "
"connection?"
msgstr ""
"Kako nastavim &Sendmail; za delovanje s &kmail;-om, če imam klicno povezavo?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First you should check to see if your distribution can do this for you. It "
"probably has already been set up during installation."
msgstr ""
"Najprej preverite, ali lahko vaša distribucija to stori. Verjetno je bilo "
"nastavljeno že med namestitvijo."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If that is not the case, you may want to have a look at <ulink url=\"https://"
"www.tldp.org/HOWTO/Mail-Queue.html\">the Mail Queue HOWTO</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"V nasprotnem primeru si lahko ogledate <ulink url=\"https://www.tldp.org/"
"HOWTO/Mail-Queue.html\"> Mail Queue HOWTO (poštna čakalna vrsta KAKO)</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I've seen demonstrations of remote control behavior with &kmail;. Is there "
"any documentation on the available interfaces?"
msgstr ""
"Videl sem predstavitve obnašanja daljinskega upravljalnika z &kmail;-om. Ali "
"obstaja dokumentacija o razpoložljivih vmesnikih?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can get a list of functions by using this command in a shell: "
"<userinput><command>qdbus</command><option>org.kde.kmail /KMail</option></"
"userinput>. Then you can control &kmail; like this: "
"<userinput><command>qdbus</command> <option>org.kde.kmail /KMail org.kde."
"kmail.kmail.folderList</option></userinput>. You can also use "
"<application>qdbusviewer</application> to browse available methods in a "
"graphical interface."
msgstr ""
"Seznam funkcij lahko dobite z uporabo tega ukaza v lupini: "
"<userinput><command>qdbus</command><option>org.kde.kmail /KMail</option></"
"userinput>. Nato lahko s &kmail;-om upravljate takole: "
"<userinput><command>qdbus</command> <option>org.kde.kmail /KMail org.kde."
"kmail.kmail.folderList</option></userinput>. Uporabite lahko tudi "
"<application>qdbusviewer</application> za pregledovanje razpoložljivih metod "
"v grafičnem vmesniku."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When I reply to a message, only a part of the message is quoted. How come?"
msgstr "Ko odgovorim na sporočilo, je citiran samo del sporočila. Kako to?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This can happen when the message contains two dashes and a space on a single "
"line. This is seen as the start of a signature. The remainder of the message "
"will not be quoted, because when you reply to a message, &kmail; strips the "
"signature."
msgstr ""
"To se lahko zgodi, če sporočilo vsebuje dva pomišljaja in presledek v eni "
"vrstici. To se šteje za začetek podpisa. Preostali del sporočila ne bo "
"citiran, ker &kmail; pri odgovarjanju na sporočilo odstrani podpis."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:672
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I am only using &IMAP;. Can I get rid of those Local Folders in the folder "
"list, or at least keep them collapsed all the time?"
msgstr ""
"Uporabljam samo &IMAP;. Ali se lahko znebim tistih lokalnih map na seznamu "
"map ali jih vsaj ves čas pustim strnjene?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No, you cannot get rid of them. The local folders function as a fallback "
"when the &IMAP; server is unreachable. Although you only use &IMAP;, &kmail; "
"uses the outbox for sending the messages. If we hide all local folders you "
"will not be able to fix messages in the outbox which cannot be send for some "
"reason. But it is possible to keep the local folders collapsed. What you "
"have to do is go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kmail;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and go "
"to the section Misc. There you can set up the folder on startup. If you "
"change that to a folder on the &IMAP; account, the Local Folders will stay "
"collapsed when &kmail; starts."
msgstr ""
"Ne, ne morete se jih znebiti. Lokalne mape delujejo kot nadomestna možnost, "
"kadar strežnik &IMAP; ni dosegljiv. Čeprav uporabljate samo &IMAP;, &kmail; "
"za pošiljanje sporočil uporablja mapo odhajajoče. Če skrijemo vse lokalne "
"mape, ne boste mogli popraviti sporočil v mapi Prejeto, ki jih iz "
"kateregakoli razloga ni mogoče poslati. Vendar pa je mogoče lokalne mape "
"ohraniti strnjene. Kar morate storiti, je, da greste v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavi &kmail;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in greste pod razdelek Razno. Tam lahko nastavite "
"mapo ob zagonu. Če jo spremenite v mapo na računu &IMAP;, bodo lokalne mape "
"ob zagonu računa &kmail; ostale zaprte."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:686
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I watch a particular thread?"
msgstr "Kako lahko gledam določeno nit?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to follow a thread, right click and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Mark Thread</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Watch Thread</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremljati nit, kliknite na desno tipko miške in izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Označi nit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Opazuj nit</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From this point on all messages on the thread that starts in this message "
"will be marked as <guilabel>Watched</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Od tega trenutka naprej bodo vsa sporočila na niti, ki se začne s tem "
"sporočilom, označena kot <guilabel>Opazovano</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I watch my own threads?"
msgstr "Ali lahko opazujem svoje lastne niti?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is useful in case you are registered to a mailing list such as kdepim-"
"users@kde.org and want to filter out the threads you participate in."
msgstr ""
"To je koristno, če ste registrirani na poštnem seznamu, kot je kdepim-"
"users@kde.org, in želite filtrirati niti, v katerih sodelujete."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a filter to mark all your incoming messages to a mailing list as "
"Watched"
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite filter za označevanje vseh prejetih sporočil na poštni seznam kot "
"Opazovana"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "To create a filter go to:"
msgstr "Če želite ustvariti filter, pojdite na:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: faq.docbook:704
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Filters</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavi filtre</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:707
#, no-c-format
msgid "select <guilabel>Match all of the following</guilabel>"
msgstr "izberite<guilabel>Naj se ujema vse od naslednjega</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:710
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add the conditions:"
msgstr "Dodajte pogoje:"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:713
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>From</guimenu><guisubmenu>Contains</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem> </guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"<replaceable>yourmail@maildomain</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Od</guimenu><guisubmenu>Vsebuje</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem> </guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"<replaceable>vašmail@domenamaila</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"replace <replaceable>yourmail@maildomain</replaceable>&nbsp;with your "
"outgoing mail address"
msgstr ""
"zamenjajte <replaceable>vašmail@domenamaila</replaceable>&nbsp; z vašim e-"
"naslovom, iz katerega pošiljate"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>List-Id</guimenu><guimenuitem>Contains</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> <replaceable>listID</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>ID-seznama</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vsebuje</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> <replaceable>ID-seznama</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"replace <replaceable>listID</replaceable> with a specific mailing list id "
"(&eg;, &lt;kdepim-users.kde.org&gt;) or just a <quote>.</quote> to include "
"outgoing mail to all mailing lists with <quote>.</quote> in their id "
"(basically all of them)."
msgstr ""
"zamenjajte <replaceable>IDseznama</replaceable> s specifičnim id-jem "
"poštnega seznama (&eg;, &lt;kdepim-users.kde.org&gt;) ali samo s <quote>.</"
"quote>, da vključite odhodno pošto na vse poštne sezname s <quote>.</quote> "
"v njihovem id-ju (torej vsemi)."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:728
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Under <guilabel>Filter Actions</guilabel> choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Mark "
"As</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Watched</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Pod <guilabel>Dejanja filtra</guilabel> izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Označi "
"kot</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Opazovano</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tab."
msgstr "V zavihku <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:737
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Uncheck <guilabel>if this filter matches, stop processing here</guilabel>, "
"so that other filters such as sorting the incoming messages from the mailing "
"list to sub-folders will execute."
msgstr ""
"Odkljukajte <guilabel>če se filter ujema, ustavi obdelavo tukaj</guilabel>, "
"da se bodo izvedli drugi filtri, kot je razvrščanje prejetih sporočil iz "
"poštnega seznama v podmape."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place that filter before other filters that may stop the filtering process, "
"or simply put it first. (Changing the filters' order is done using the two "
"arrows up and down, under the <guilabel>Available filters</guilabel> list.)"
msgstr ""
"Postavite ta filter pred druge filtre, ki lahko ustavijo postopek "
"filtriranja, ali pa ga preprosto postavite na prvo mesto. (Vrstni red "
"filtrov spremenite s puščicama navzgor in navzdol pod seznamom "
"<guilabel>Dostopni filtri</guilabel>.)"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a search on mailing list messages"
msgstr "Ustvarite iskanje po sporočilih poštnega seznama"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the folder where your mailing list messages are stored (&eg;, Local "
"Folders/KDE-PIM-USERS) and hit <keycap>S</keycap> key or in the menu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Messages</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>:"
msgstr ""
"Pojdite v mapo, v kateri so shranjena sporočila vašega poštnega seznama "
"(&eg;, Local Folders/KDE-PIM-USERS), in pritisnite tipko <keycap>S</keycap> "
"ali v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Poišči "
"sporočila</guimenuitem></menuchoice>:"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:754
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select <guilabel>Match all of the following</guilabel>"
msgstr "Izberite <guilabel>Naj se ujema vse od naslednjega</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:754
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pay attention to the <guilabel>Include sub-folders</guilabel>."
msgstr "Bodite pozorni na <guilabel>Vključi podmape</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:758
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add the condition: <menuchoice><guimenu>Message Status</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>is</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Watched</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Dodajte pogoj: <menuchoice><guimenu>Stanje sporočila</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>je</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Opazovano</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Give the search an informative name (<guilabel>Search folder name</"
"guilabel>) like <replaceable>KDE-PIM-USERS-Watched</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"Iskanju dajte informativno ime (<guilabel>Ime mape iskanj</guilabel>), na "
"primer <replaceable>KDE-PIM-USERS-Watched</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid "Make the search. After it is done you can close the search window."
msgstr "Izvedite iskanje. Po končanem iskanju lahko okno za iskanje zaprete."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now whenever you start a thread or participate in one, it is "
"<guilabel>Watched</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Sedaj je nit, ki jo začnete ali v njej sodelujete, <guilabel>Opazovana</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:777
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I use E-Mail Translation?"
msgstr "Lahko uporabljam prevajanje e-pošte?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To translate text in the composer window read the section <link linkend="
"\"using-the-translator\">Using the Built-in Translator</link>"
msgstr ""
"Za prevajanje besedila v oknu skladatelja, preberite odsek<link linkend="
"\"using-the-translator\">Uporaba vgrajenega prevajalnika</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:781
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the message preview pane highlight the text you would like to translate "
"and select <guimenuitem>Translate</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>) from the &RMB; context menu."
msgstr ""
"V podoknu za predogled sporočila označite besedilo, ki ga želite prevesti, "
"in izberite <guimenuitem>Prevedi</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>) v kontekstnem meniju &RMB;."

